# Design System Enforcer

- Use only these CSS variables (tokens). Do not hardcode hex/rgb elsewhere.
- Base: `--color-base` #0B1020
- Surface: `--color-surface` #111A33
- Accent mint: `--color-accent-mint` #00D1B2
- Accent orange: `--color-accent-orange` #FF6B35
- Text primary: `--color-text-primary` #EAF2FF
- Text secondary: `--color-text-secondary` #A9B6CC
